Officially I’m a internationally certified makeup artist now🔥

  I often strive to learn something new about makeup from the masters in this industry, and so I end up joining so many master classes just to learn new techniques and gain knowledge. Eventually, I believed that it would help me to provide the best service from my side to the clients. Even this plan to join his master class was started like that. But the knowledge I gained from him was beyond what I imagined. This class was like a full meal for a hungry human🔥. Every moment, I learned a new thing from him. I never imagined that this master class would completely change my makeup game🔥. Thank you, master, for teaching us these many techniques. Not just makeup; you also taught us to be disciplined. We promise you that we will follow those principles💯. The class was completely satisfying. My heartfelt thanks to you, @kannanraajamanickam ♥️ and S4 Events @s4_wellness ♥️ for making this happen. 🫶🏻🦋♥️

#thankugod #thanksfortheuniverse 
Spl thanks to my family, friends, followers and well wishes for supporting my dream♥️ 🥺
